data.description: You definitely want to check this home out! Move-in ready 4 bedroom home situated in a cul-de sac, featuring a massive backyard perfect for fun and entertaining. Split level floor plan with plenty of living space, hardwood floors throughout the main level, and a fireplace, perfect for cool fall evenings. Primary bedroom with private access to the back deck, walk in closet, and en-suite bathroom with dual sinks, soaker tub and separate shower. Spacious eat-in kitchen, and a formal dining room. Two additional bedrooms on the main level, 4th bedroom is on the lower level, as well as a spacious bonus area. Large laundry area, 2 car attached garage with plenty of storage space, and a massive. fully fenced backyard!
